data.description: Looking for a fixer upper in Lockport, this spacious 4 bedroom 2 bath may be exactly what you're looking for. The home was previously a duplex and could easily be converted back. The home features a new corrugated metal roof, new electrical panel/wiring and newer HVAC(2021). The possibilities are endless and just waiting on someone to put their special touch on it. Call today to schedule your private showing.
